column2: In Barad-Dur, many of your most capable lieutenants reside. They handle the daily tasks of running your realm, and keep your unruly legions under control.

column2: You have gathered to yourself an inner circle, loyal only to yourself. These include orcs, Uruk-Hai, Half-Orcs, and Dunlendings. They take care of all the drudgery associated with ruling a realm and building armies.
